{"tid":2368141,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"行會成員表示：美國制裁係無牙老虎 對大家生活毫無影響","createTime":"2021-01-16T02:42:25.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-16T03:58:58.000Z","uid":19552,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"b09b5bc0e1c503bcca6f48dfbcee22bdb5a1c0b6","tid":2368141,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-16T02:42:25.000Z","msg":"行會成員回應本報提問如下：<br />\n問：有否資產在美國？會否擔心被制裁？<br />\n<br />\n葉劉淑儀：我一點都不擔心。基於私隱理由，私人財產安排不會公開交代。<br />\n湯家驊：我無資產，亦不擔心。<br />\n羅范椒芬：行會成員應該不會被制裁，我在美國亦沒有資產。<br />\n黃國健：我有少少美元存款，毋須擔心。如果有幸能成為被制裁的對象，這是我的榮幸！可惜我這種小角色不配。<br />\n葉國謙：相信中央政府會有回應。我無資產在美國，亦不會到美國；若美國要制裁行會成員，制裁到夠囉。<br />\n劉業強：我在美國沒有任何資產，對於現在中美角力戰不斷升溫，經濟將大受影響，受害的必然是一般市民百姓，所以我更關注的是一般市民尤其基層的生活狀況。"},{"pid":"10e4440a426b92734a57d0dc5c88a7c6c94ccccc","tid":2368141,"uid":2054,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-16T02:43:42.000Z","msg":"湯家驊：我無資產，亦不擔心。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d6cb4d85ec065d2d101632d1b638574a98ffa0a","tid":2368141,"uid":36497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-16T02:43:45.000Z","msg":"呢班人剩係識9up 未輪到佢地啦"},{"pid":"b9e7334c3a1bf0b28f4ab756e4fcc83a6ef90e5e","tid":2368141,"uid":19552,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"10e4440a426b92734a57d0dc5c88a7c6c94ccccc","tid":2368141,"uid":2054,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-16T02:43:42.000Z","msg":"湯家驊：我無資產，亦不擔心。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-16T02:44:23.000Z","msg":"學林鄭現金出糧<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />衰過破產"},{"pid":"1fcd42a81c78e9b24c11165ab82b1be3e826d4f0","tid":2368141,"uid":283207,"like":0,"disl